############################
Break Root Password
############################
1-interrupt boot process 
2-choose the 2nd choice in boot menu
3-press  " e "
4-go to line start with linux   then press "end" and write down rd.break
5-ctrl+x 
6-press enter then write $mount -oremount,rw /sysroot 
7-$chroot /sysroot 
8- $passwd 
9-enter the new password
10-$touch /.autorelabel
11-$exit
12-$exit
